imperial-medieval-flavor = Character description
imperial-medieval-flavor-help = Clicking on the square with the image allows you to set a new character image.
    Inappropriate or offensive images may result in restrictions, including permanent bans.
    The image can have your character, preferably in a portrait view.
    The rule regarding the use of popular/public figures also applies to images.
    {"The image must be 256x256 pixels."}
